<item>
            <title>[LU-4182] sanity-scrub test_15: FAIL: (10) Failed to start OI scrub on mds1 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4182</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for wangdi &amp;lt;di.wang@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/db440b32-40b9-11e3-a1e8-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/db440b32-40b9-11e3-a1e8-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_15 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CMD: wtm-23vm3 /usr/sbin/lctl lfsck_start -M lustre-MDT0000 10 -n on&lt;br/&gt;
wtm-23vm3: Fail to start LFSCK: Operation already in progress&lt;br/&gt;
 sanity-scrub test_15: @@@@@@ FAIL: (10) Failed to start OI scrub on mds1 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-scrub 15&lt;/p&gt;</description>
