                            <comment id="142136" author="yong.fan" created="Sat, 13 Feb 2016 06:19:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It worked well in my local VM environment. I will make patch to enable test_15 under DNE mode.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="142132" author="adilger" created="Sat, 13 Feb 2016 04:43:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The test is currently always being skipped for DNE configuration:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;test_15() {
        # skip test_15 for LU-4182
        [ $MDSCOUNT -ge 2 ] &amp;amp;&amp;amp; skip &quot;skip now for &amp;gt;= 2 MDTs&quot; &amp;amp;&amp;amp; return
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;so bug cannot be closed.  As a starting point, please submit a patch to remove this line and allow it to be tested in DNE mode.  Then, if it passes the patch can be landed, and if not you will have information for debugging it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="142126" author="adilger" created="Sat, 13 Feb 2016 03:22:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fan Yong, is there some way to test the functionality for test_15 even if multiple MDTs are configured?  That would allow &lt;tt&gt;sanity-scrub&lt;/tt&gt; to be removed from &lt;tt&gt;review-ldiskfs&lt;/tt&gt; and only be tested as part of &lt;tt&gt;review-dne-part-2&lt;/tt&gt; and save us 30 minutes of testing time per patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="142124" author="yong.fan" created="Sat, 13 Feb 2016 02:54:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is too long time ago the failures happened, but without logs. It is almost impossible to analysis that.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Related troubles may have been fixed in the past two years. We have not hit the same/similar troubles for a long time.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can close it. If reproduced in future, reopen it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
